Package: outlierPlot
Title: Interactive Diagnostic Plots for Linear and Logistic Models
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Johann",
           family = "Popp",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "johann.popp@posteo.de")
Description: 
    Produces a set of interactive diagnostic plots. Brushing outstandig
    cases in one plot highlights the same cases in the other plots.
    Raw data of the brushed cases is shown. An alternative model excluding
    the brushed cases is calculated and compared to the original model.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.1.1
Depends: 
    R (>= 3.0.2), stats
Imports: 
    ggplot2 (>= 2.2.1),
    shiny (>= 1.0.5),
    grid,
    htmltools
URL: https://github.com/JohannPopp/outlierPlot

